snippet.title: TOY DIVISION LIVE! Pre Kempton Park toy fair and the weekly toy hunt reveals
snippet.description:
Welcome back everyone to the this weeks toy hunting podcast TOY DIVISION LIVE! 
On the show this week we will be chatting about the weekend toy hunting trips, toy hauls, up coming toy shows and prepping this weekends Kempton Park toy fair. 

JOIN TOY DIVISION TODAY! THIS THE WAY.
